The Committee shall consist of—
* the Secretary to the Treasury, or his representative;
	* the Secretary for Economic Planning and Development, or his representative;
	* the Secretary for Works, or his representative;
	* the Secretary for Agriculture, or his representative;
	* the Secretary for Forestry and Natural Resources, or his representative;
	* the Secretary for Transport and Communications, or his representative;
	* the Inspector General of Police, or his representative;
	* the Army Commander, or his representative;
	* the Secretary for Youth and Culture or his representative;
	* not less than three and not more than five other members representing the non-governmental sector appointed by the Minister.
